
Chennai Rental Agency is Involved in Giving Items on Rent

They Rent the following Products

1) Electrical Items Like : Fan,Mixie,Grinder etc

2) Electronic Items Like : Speaker, Microphone etc.,

3) Furniture Items Like : Sofa, Bed, Carpet,Shamiana,Chairs etc.


They Rent Items on Daily or Monthly Basis

The Rent is calculated based on the Item Type

For Electrical - Its Rs.30/- per day and a discount of 10% for monthly

For Electronic - Its Rs.50/ per day and discount of 5% for monthly

For Furniture - Its Rs.70 per day and discount of 15% for monthly


Write a Java Application Using Interface Based Design and a Factory

Method to implements the above Problem statement



